# Console live E2E gate artifacts (issue #3326): screenshots, Playwright trace,
# JSON report, logs, and the local-only env file with the throwaway API key.
# Durable LOCAL proof only; never commit binaries or the local key.
e2e-artifacts/

# Claude Code per-user overrides; .claude/settings.json is committed so the
# project hook works for everyone who clones.
.claude/settings.local.json

# Stray compiled cmd binaries from a bare `go build ./cmd/<name>` (build to a tmp dir instead)
/go/capability-inventory
